channel.title: The Guild
channel.description:
A sitcom webisode about a group of online gamers.

www.watchtheguild.com for more details!

Created and starring Felicia Day - Buffy's (Vi)

Directed by Jane Selle Morgan - seejanedirect.com and Greg Benson - mediocrefilms.com

Produced by Felicia Day, Kim Evey - creator of Gorgeous Tiny Chicken Machine Show and Jane Selle Morgan.
channel.itunes:summary: The Guild is a independent sitcom webisode in the style of "The Office" about a group of online gamers who play together in a World of Warcraft-like fantasy world.
channel.itunes:author: Watch The Guild
